dm\_industrial (rev#GAMMA), by warhawk3407
=========================================

Compilation settings :
----------------------
BSP  = "Normal" Vvis = "Normal" Vrad = "Normal" HDR = "ON"

Features :
----------
Map overview & RADAR! SNOWFALL! 3D SKYBOX! Advanced lighting! NAV file included! Cube maps (reflects)!

Map inspired by the gameplay of aim\_ag\_texture2, and by the design of cs\_office or cs\_assault.
